### =========================================================
### PRODUCT API
### =========================================================

### Create product (happy path)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "SKU-001",
  "name": "Producto de prueba",
  "price": 19.99
}

### Create product (duplicate SKU → 409)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "SKU-001",
  "name": "Producto duplicado",
  "price": 9.99
}

### Create product (validation error → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "",
  "name": "",
  "price": -10
}

### Get paged products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products?page=0&size=10

### Get product by id (happy path)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/1

### Get product by id (not found → 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/99999


### =========================================================
### INVENTORY API
### =========================================================

### Get inventory by sku (initial state)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001

### Restock inventory (happy path)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001/restock?quantity=10

### Get inventory after restock
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001

### Reserve inventory (happy path)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001/reserve?quantity=5

### Get inventory after reserve
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001

### Reserve inventory (insufficient stock → 409)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001/reserve?quantity=20

### Get inventory after failed reserve (should be unchanged)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001


### =========================================================
### INVENTORY VALIDATION / EDGE CASES
### =========================================================

### Restock inventory (invalid quantity → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001/restock?quantity=0

### Reserve inventory (invalid quantity → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-001/reserve?quantity=-3

### Get inventory for non-existent SKU (404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/SKU-DOES-NOT-EXIST
